#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.p:11-7
msgid ""
"With so many features and keystrokes available between JAWS, Windows, and "
"the various Office apps, it can be challenging to locate the information you "
"need to perform a specific task or even look up a setting or keystroke you "
"no longer recall. The new AI assistant, FSCompanion, lets you ask questions "
"about JAWS and other applications and quickly provides the information you "
"need without you having to search through multiple documents and web pages "
"to find it. Want to know how a particular JAWS feature works, or the "
"sequence of keystrokes to perform a specific task in Word? Ask FSCompanion, "
"and the AI searches through various help and training resources in a matter "
"of seconds, and provides the key details in a concise step-by-step format."
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.p:12-1
msgid ""
"FSCompanion has been trained using JAWS help and training data as well as "
"support content from other sources."
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.p:13-1
msgid ""
"FSCompanion is capable of responding to questions about the following, with "
"an emphasis on providing specific keystrokes as answers."
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:15-1
msgid "JAWS usage"
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:16-1
msgid "Windows usage and navigation"
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:17-1
msgid "Web browsing"
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:18-1
msgid "Microsoft Office applications (Word, Excel, Outlook, and PowerPoint)"
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:19-1
msgid ""
"Google Workspace applications (Gmail, Chrome, Drive, Docs, Sheets, and "
"Slides)"
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.p:21-1
msgid "To open FSCompanion, do one of the following:"
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:23-1
msgid ""
"In JAWS, press the layered command, <strong>INSERT+SPACEBAR</strong>, "
"followed by <strong>F1</strong>. FSCompanion is also located in the JAWS "
"Help menu under Web Resources."
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:24-1
msgid ""
"Open FSCompanion using the JAWS Voice Assistant. For instance, you can say "
"“hey Sharky, open FSCompanion.”"
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:25-1
msgid ""
"Go to <a href=\"https://fscompanion.ai\" target=\"_blank\">FSCompanion.ai</"
"a> from a PC or mobile device using your preferred web browser."
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.p:27-1
msgid ""
"Once the FSCompanion page opens, press <strong>TAB</strong> to move to the "
"edit field and type a question. After typing a question, press "
"<strong>ENTER</strong>, and JAWS will automatically read the response as "
"soon as it is displayed. Focus remains in the edit field, so you can ask any "
"follow-up questions."
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.p:28-1
msgid ""
"You also have the option to speak your questions. Press <strong>ALT+SHIFT+D</"
"strong>, or use the Dictate button to start dictating to FSCompanion. Press "
"<strong>ALT+SHIFT+D</strong> again, or use the Stop dictation button to "
"stop. The dictated text will appear in the input edit box for review."
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.p:29-1
msgid ""
"To review answers, use <strong>H</strong>, <strong>SHIFT+H</strong>, or the "
"<strong>ARROW</strong> keys. Select the <strong>New Conversation</strong> "
"button to start a new topic, or select the <strong>Feedback</strong> button "
"to submit any comments about a response."
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.p:30-1
msgid "Here are a few example questions to help get you started."
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:32-1
msgid "How do I change the JAWS volume?"
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:33-1
msgid "How do I select cells in Excel?"
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:34-1
msgid "How do I turn off the Preview Pane in Outlook?"
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:35-1
msgid "How do I select text?"
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.ul.li:36-1
msgid "How do I set a PlaceMarker on a page?"
msgstr ""

#: HTM_po_nelkul%5CFSCompanion.htm%2Bhtml.body.p:38-1
msgid ""
"Please ask as many questions as you like, and don’t hesitate to give "
"feedback on your experiences. The types of questions you ask and the "
"feedback you provide are very important as it helps our team train the model "
"to be more accurate."
msgstr ""

